sqlParams.paramVal: SELECT 'MAX_KEY' AS max_key, COALESCE(MAX(person_key) ,0) FROM dim_person;

properties.propertyVal:
DI_CF(
SRC_person_ods.person_pid IS NOT NULL 
AND SRC_person_ods.is_current  = 1 )

SELECT distinct
	SRC_person_ods.P_KEY AS P_KEY
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_PID AS PERSON_PID
	,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.FIRST_NAME), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR) AS FIRST_NAME
	,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.LAST_NAME), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR) AS LAST_NAME
	,SRC_person_ods.MIDDLE_INITIAL AS MIDDLE_INITIAL
	,SRC_person_ods.NICKNAME AS NICKNAME
	,SRC_person_ods.DOB AS DOB
	,SRC_person_ods.GENDER AS GENDER
	,SRC_person_ods.TIME_ZONE AS TIME_ZONE
	,SRC_person_ods.BEST_TIME_TO_CALL AS BEST_TIME_TO_CALL
	,SRC_person_ods.BEST_TIME_TO_CALL_NOTE AS BEST_TIME_TO_CALL_NOTE
	,SRC_person_ods.OK_TO_LEAVE_MESSAGE AS OK_TO_LEAVE_MESSAGE
	,SRC_person_ods.EMAIL_OPT_OUT AS EMAIL_OPT_OUT
	,SRC_person_ods.PHONE_OPT_OUT AS PHONE_OPT_OUT
	,SRC_person_ods.SMS_OPT_OUT AS SMS_OPT_OUT
	,SRC_person_ods.MAIL_OPT_OUT AS MAIL_OPT_OUT
	,SRC_person_ods.IS_DELETED AS IS_DELETED
	,SRC_person_ods.DELETED_BY AS DELETED_BY
	,SRC_person_ods.DELETED_AT AS DELETED_AT
	,SRC_person_ods.DSDQ_REASON_PID AS DSDQ_REASON_PID
	,SRC_person_ods.DSDQ_REASON AS DSDQ_REASON
	,SRC_person_ods.DSDQ_REASON_DESC AS DSDQ_REASON_DESC
	,SRC_person_ods.DSDQ_REASON_NOTE AS DSDQ_REASON_NOTE
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_LANGUAGE AS PERSON_LANGUAGE
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_RACE AS PERSON_RACE
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ETHNICITY AS PERSON_ETHNICITY
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_STATUS AS PERSON_EMPLOYMENT_STATUS
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_MARITAL_STATUS AS PERSON_MARITAL_STATUS
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_PSYCHG_PROFILE AS PERSON_PSYCHG_PROFILE
	,SRC_person_ods.MP_UUID AS MP_UUID
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_NOTE AS PERSON_NOTE
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_TYPE AS PERSON_ADDRESS_TYPE
	,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS1), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR)  AS PERSON_ADDRESS1
	,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS2), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR)  AS PERSON_ADDRESS2
	,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_CITY), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR)  AS PERSON_ADDRESS_CITY
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_STATE AS PERSON_ADDRESS_STATE
	,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_POSTAL_CODE), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR)  AS PERSON_ADDRESS_POSTAL_CODE
        ,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTY), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR)   AS PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTY
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTRY AS PERSON_ADDRESS_COUNTRY
        ,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_LATITUDE), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR)  AS PERSON_ADDRESS_LATITUDE
        ,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_LONGITUDE), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR)  AS PERSON_ADDRESS_LONGITUDE
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_NOTE AS PERSON_ADDRESS_NOTE
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_START_DATE AS PERSON_ADDRESS_START_DATE
	,SRC_person_ods.PERSON_ADDRESS_END_DATE AS PERSON_ADDRESS_END_DATE
        ,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_EMAIL), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR) AS PERSON_EMAIL
        ,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_HOME_PHONE), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR) AS PERSON_HOME_PHONE
        ,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_ods.PERSON_MOBILE_PHONE), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR) AS PERSON_MOBILE_PHONE
	,SRC_person_ods.SRC_CREATED_AT AS SRC_CREATED_AT
	,SRC_person_ods.SRC_CREATED_BY AS SRC_CREATED_BY
	,SRC_person_ods.SRC_UPDATED_AT AS SRC_UPDATED_AT
	,SRC_person_ods.SRC_UPDATED_BY AS SRC_UPDATED_BY
	,SRC_person_ods.CREATED_AT AS CREATED_AT
	,SRC_person_ods.UPDATED_AT AS UPDATED_AT
	,SRC_person_ods.VERSION AS VERSION
	,SRC_person_ods.IS_CURRENT AS IS_CURRENT
	,CAST('V4' AS CHAR) AS SOURCE_SYSTEM
	,TRIM(CAST(SRC_person_ods.person_pid  AS CHAR)) AS V_PERSON_PID
	,CAST(SRC_person_ods.ok_to_leave_message AS SIGNED) AS V_OK_TO_LEAVE_MESSAGE
	,CAST(SRC_person_ods.mail_opt_out AS SIGNED) AS V_EMAIL_OPT_OUT
	,CAST(SRC_person_ods.phone_opt_out AS SIGNED) AS V_PHONE_OPT_OUT
	,CAST(SRC_person_ods.sms_opt_out  AS SIGNED) AS V_SMS_OPT_OUT
	,CAST(SRC_person_ods.mail_opt_out  AS SIGNED) AS V_MAIL_OPT_OUT
	,0 AS V_IS_DELETED
	,CAST('' as CHAR) AS V_ENGAGEMENT_HLTHSEG
        ,CAST(AES_DECRYPT(UNHEX(SRC_person_client_ods.MEMBER_ID), UNHEX(SHA2($PP_V4_ODS_DECRYPT_KEY,512))) AS CHAR) as MEMBER_ID 
	 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MY_BOLD_ODS_PERSON_ODS SRC_person_ods 
        left join person_client_ods SRC_person_client_ods  on SRC_person_ods.person_pid=SRC_person_client_ods.person_pid
        WHERE SRC_person_ods.person_pid IS NOT NULL  AND SRC_person_ods.is_current  = 1  and  (SRC_person_client_ods.person_pid IS NOT NULL  AND SRC_person_client_ods.is_current  = 1)

dCmd_Inst.dCmd:
UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'SUCCEEDED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
SRC_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS.SRC_person_ods.SourceCount   , 
SRC_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS.SRC_person_ods.ProcessCount  , 
SRC_target_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS.SRC_person_ods.TargetCount  , 
SRC_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS.SRC_person_ods.BadCount  ,
TGT_source_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS.TGT_dim_person.SourceCount   , 
TGT_process_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS.TGT_dim_person.ProcessCount  , 
TGT_target_count  =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS.TGT_dim_person.TargetCount   , 
TGT_bad_count =  $RST_DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS.TGT_dim_person.BadCount   ,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'FAILED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING'

INSERT INTO control_load_history (data_flow_name, status, start_timestamp, created_at)
VALUES ('DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS', 'RUNNING', $$CurrentTimeStamp, $$CurrentTimeStamp);

UPDATE control_load_history
SET status = 'ABORTED', 
finish_timestamp = $$CurrentTimeStamp,
updated_at = $$CurrentTimeStamp
WHERE data_flow_name = 'DF_LOAD_dim_person_V4_ODS' AND status= 'RUNNING';
